{"tid":2069176,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"電影已成權鬥工具 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-06-18T07:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T07:56:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2d4b0024e620e2c4e8349639658634d1be4bfc","tid":2069176,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:56:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200618/20939180/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200618%2F20939180%2F&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHg4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=263569bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200618%2F20939180%2F&h=7d26bd6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200618/20939180/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n電影已成權鬥工具 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200618/large/1592376946_8f59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200618%2Flarge%2F1592376946_8f59.jpg&h=6746c211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《蘋果日報》截圖<br />\n<br />\n擺地攤就擺地攤，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，還有活路？<br />\n<br />\n習大大要在今年決勝全面實現小康社會，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。；論權，則完敗。<br />\n<br />\n習李鬥我們不關注，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，文化藝術影視就得統一口徑附和。<br />\n<br />\n為了加強習大大權威，中宣部掌控的電影局立刻下達命令，拍攝主旋律影片《我和我的家鄉》，故事主題就是老百姓歡欣鼓舞迎小康之家；好讓全國觀眾忘了李總理的真心話，只記習主席虛幻綺夢。當然得是輕鬆喜劇，5個單元湊份兒，城鄉發展好，國家愈富強──好一劑麻醉藥，一道催眠靈符。<br />\n<br />\n北京朋友還道，是《我和我的祖國》倒模作，國慶檔期上。「祖國」是什麼片港人不知，且編導演很多拿外國護照的。後作「家鄉」亦陌生，只幕後都是大卡，如張藝謀寧浩鄧超徐崢等。中國大陸的電影已成權鬥工具，若香港淪陷，港人便要看這些啦。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}